metadata.name: Dirt x Bloomers
metadata.description:
Dirt is a daily(ish) newsletter about digital pop culture and entertainment.

Bloomers is an edition of 1,111 generative flowers minting at <https://www.bloomers.life/>

Each layer is hand drawn and generated into unique combinations of ecosystems, beings and colors.

Bloomers on Twitter: <https://twitter.com/bloomers_nft>

Blooms on Foundation: <https://foundation.app/collection/bloomers>

Secretsower on Foundation: <https://foundation.app/@Secretsower>
